{"tid":1267330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登變成一個點既地方?","createTime":"2019-06-29T20:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T23:34:29.000Z","uid":6237,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a5a649e5dac3fea90519a5d3f6292efa5908e03","tid":1267330,"uid":6237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:56:27.000Z","msg":"變成一個一唔啱心意就屌既地方<br />\n變成一個和理非既地方<br />\n<br />\n當初連登都唔係因為和理非先得番黎<br />\n好多人係今次抗爭做埋啲無為野<br />\n寫心意紙 藝術創作又性<br />\n<br />\n啱啱有人話記念跳樓既青年既方法會破壞環境<br />\n講一下比人話三毛仲要有成300幾個like<br />\n<br />\n可想而知呢個地方已經變咗大台<br />\n我其實真係唔介意有人睇完負評我<br />\n<br />\n老實講句, 除咗勇務既人做到暫緩條例外<br />\n其實又登報又圍又性, 得到既係咩?<br />\n方法有好多, 但一定唔係咁溫和先<br />\n咁同五年前有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家話我三毛<br />\n我寧願悲觀都唔想開心登個8個頭版打飛機"},{"pid":"12d48fd96a5867b2f83f6af37cffbb93f5ee5ecd","tid":1267330,"uid":45007,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:59:57.000Z","msg":"我繼續會岀<br />\n直至真係完全無人為止<br />\n人地呀婆咁老都撐到<br />\n你同我後生仔唔可以埋怨咁多<br />\n和理非係多 但始終係同路人<br />\n不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"7589c82b61b218d22f99e4b1776bc803c2bf2ca1","tid":1267330,"uid":233325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:00:03.000Z","msg":"唔好再分化勇武同和理非<br />\n得唔得"},{"pid":"5368759d767c6316698644818af3b7dd0fd472b5","tid":1267330,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:02:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請自行判斷<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCbJY3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCbJY3P.jpg&h=8067287b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f90500af6b4e7257817cecb0001f95a86452419","tid":1267330,"uid":6237,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"5368759d767c6316698644818af3b7dd0fd472b5","tid":1267330,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:02:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請自行判斷<br />\n</span></span><br